import React from 'react';

import {
  Button,
  Flex,
  Image,
  Menu,
  MenuButton,
  MenuItem,
  MenuList,
} from '@chakra-ui/core';

const Header: React.FC = () => (
  <Flex width="100vw" height={85} backgroundColor="#Blue.300">
    <Image
      src="http://lafengenharia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/cropped-MARCA_LAFE_CHAPADA.png"
      width={180}
    />

    <Menu>
      <MenuButton>
        <Flex
          borderColor="blue.300"
          border="2px solid "
          borderRadius="50%"
          width={10}
          height={10}
        >
          <Image
            borderRadius="50%"
            src="https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/57292850?s=460&u=c239cda75c724d55793087628b4276330ae99942&v=4"
          />
        </Flex>
      </MenuButton>
      <MenuList>
        <MenuItem>Download</MenuItem>
        <MenuItem>Create a Copy</MenuItem>
        <MenuItem>Mark as Draft</MenuItem>
        <MenuItem>Delete</MenuItem>
        <MenuItem>Attend a Workshop</MenuItem>
      </MenuList>
    </Menu>
  </Flex>
);

export default Header;
